  "text": "To determine the cross-correlations, we first go to the frame of reference where the rotational-rotational part of the mobility matrix is diagonal, and evaluate the correlation matrix C diag in this frame, using the explicit expressions from [CITATION_1] . Then, with the use of the 3 × 3 transformation matrix T , we transform it to the original frame of reference,",
